name: Sunny Blackbird
description: A Red-winged Blackbird on a sunny day to bring you a bit of light.  One of the first signs of spring, and a sure bet at reedy ponds, but they’ll clean out your feeders too! | Photographed May 19, 2020 at Fresh Pond in Cambridge, MA | 2150 × 1689px | @PapaBeardedNFTs
